## Epic List

## Epic List

### Epic 1: Authentication, Identity & Organization Setup
Users can securely register, login, configure MFA, and establish their organizational profile and RBAC structures. Provides the foundation for tenant-isolated data.
**FRs covered:** FR6, FR16, FR27, FR35, FR37, FR53, FR68, FR69, FR80, FR91, FR108, FR112, FR113, FR123, FR128, FR130, FR133, FR134, FR143, FR149, FR151, FR152, FR153, FR156, FR158, FR159, FR161, FR163, FR17, FR30, FR31, FR34, FR42, FR44, FR45, FR47, FR48, FR49, FR50, FR52, FR60, FR62, FR63, FR66, FR67, FR71, FR76, FR77, FR78, FR79, FR83, FR86, FR89, FR94, FR96, FR97, FR98, FR100, FR106, FR109, FR122, FR140, FR141, FR150, FR154

### Epic 2: Opportunity Intelligence & Discovery
Users can automatically discover relevant procurement and grant opportunities from AOP, TED, and EU portals, matched to their organizational profile using AI scoring.
**FRs covered:** FR1, FR2, FR3, FR5, FR8, FR9, FR13, FR14, FR15, FR18, FR36, FR38, FR41, FR43, FR46, FR51, FR55, FR56, FR57, FR58, FR59, FR61, FR70, FR74, FR82, FR85, FR95, FR101, FR102, FR103, FR104, FR105, FR110, FR114, FR115, FR119, FR124, FR127, FR129, FR138, FR145, FR146, FR147, FR148, FR155, FR160, FR162

### Epic 3: Tender Document Analysis & Extraction
Users can upload and analyze complex tender documents, automatically extracting executive summaries, technical requirements, and compliance checklists.
**FRs covered:** FR4, FR10, FR12, FR23, FR25, FR64, FR75, FR87, FR99, FR111, FR116, FR117, FR118, FR120, FR121, FR142

### Epic 4: Bid Strategy, Risk & Feasibility
Users receive AI-driven bid/no-bid recommendations based on risk analysis, financial capability matching, and competitor analytics before investing resources.
**FRs covered:** FR26, FR32, FR33, FR54, FR65, FR125, FR126, FR135, FR137, FR144, FR157

### Epic 5: Proposal Planning & Resource Allocation
Users can plan out the proposal workflow by building Gantt timelines, defining work packages, structuring compliant budgets, and finding consortium partners.
**FRs covered:** FR7, FR20, FR131, FR136

### Epic 6: Collaborative Proposal Drafting
Users can collaboratively draft proposals with AI assistance, track version history, leave comments, and ensure consistent styling across sections.
**FRs covered:** FR21, FR22, FR24, FR28, FR29, FR73, FR88, FR92, FR93

### Epic 7: Compliance, Review & Export
Users can validate their draft against compliance frameworks, fill out standard forms (like ESPD), and export a final, perfectly formatted document package for submission.
**FRs covered:** FR11, FR19, FR40, FR72, FR81, FR107, FR139

### Epic 8: Analytics, Learning & Optimization
Users can track win/loss outcomes, generate post-bid 'lessons learned' reports, and monitor organizational performance across multiple bids.
**FRs covered:** FR39, FR84, FR90, FR132



